{
  "stem": "27507.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that gate which was open, there was a bakery there, and two big blokes, bakers, were standing-- and a Jewish policeman-- were standing blocking the entrance to the gate.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as it happened, the chap who went-- who walked immediately after us was some judenrat man, some judenrat official, with this little boy, was his son, who was walking immediately past us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he knew the name of this policeman who was standing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He probably knew most of the Jewish policeman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He knew the name of the one who was standing there in the gate, and he shouted to him, shouted something like his name.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it was something like Sosnofski.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The gate opened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can I come in?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Something like that, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that all happened in very quickly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when he shouted it, the Ukrainian who was running around somewhere came and started beating him up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my cousin, who had very quick orientation, at the same moment jumped out of the march, out of the line of people, and he pulled his-- the other cousin, the girl, after him, and she pulled me, and we all three ran towards the gate.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not far, because we were after all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We ran towards the gate, and he hit the-- one of the bakers, I think, with his head, and the baker folded up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we all burst into the gate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after us, we had a lot of screaming and shouting and more people came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- there must have been something like 20 people who burst out of the march, and they all came after us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somehow there was terrible chaos and shooting, but they obviously didn't have enough people leading the march to start bothering after running and finding us.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
